      "text": "Overregulation threatens lobstering families and fishing communities up and down our coast, and I’m spending the rest of my time in Congress working to make sure this way of life has a future in Maine that’s just as vibrant as its past. \n\nI recently sat down with @fishstewardship https://t.co/W64S6iCW2b",
