      "text": "I share the grief of those mourning the loss of Searsmont Assistant Fire Chief Wayne Woodbury, who passed away yesterday morning from injuries sustained combatting the fire at Robbins Lumber a month ago.\n\nAssistant Chief Woodbury was a hero who died in the line of service",
