      "text": "Last night, I signed @RepFletcher's Discharge Petition to force a vote on the Right to Contraception Act. \n\nAll Americans have a right to decide for themselves whether, how and when to grow their families. The Supreme Court recognized the right to contraception in the ‘60s. But https://t.co/HUPh2KC4KV",
